{"tid":1776342,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"求救! 可能係恐嚇","createTime":"2019-12-09T12:50:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-09T13:12:19.000Z","uid":341380,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"d8bfc744ebfe389181461918c88dd314b8bc0d3c","tid":1776342,"uid":341380,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T12:50:24.000Z","msg":"有無人收過呢啲電話<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />:我<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />大陸口音男人<br />\n<br />\n突然有把大陸口音嘅男人打嚟同我講<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />:點啊，認唔認得我啊 (我個英文名)<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />:你係？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />:真係唔認得我？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />:邊位？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />:哈哈哈<br />\n<br />\n佢笑左幾聲之後收左線<br />\n我以為係嗰啲呃錢電話，但呢個唔同，佢知道埋我英文名<br />\n<br />\n真心，有啲驚<br />\n<br />\n晏晝仲收到啲咩中移動話我電話異常使用，但我無理到，唔知有無關係。<br />\n<br />\n我嘗試打返俾佢，但響左一陣就好似啲離島線咁斷左線<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zYhP6YX.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzYhP6YX.png&h=f55bc272&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9b38961630389832e7182b94168451cd0f2c51a5","tid":1776342,"uid":341380,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T12:51:28.000Z","msg":"未試過收呢啲電話，有無人同我一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"12a550cc18527ddb6953782f8c0b7d4fa9f0e533","tid":1776342,"uid":179979,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T12:54:44.000Z","msg":"你英文名多唔多人用？"},{"pid":"3db50b539163706c6cf3017cf6f64e12d255e030","tid":1776342,"uid":341380,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"12a550cc18527ddb6953782f8c0b7d4fa9f0e533","tid":1776342,"uid":179979,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T12:54:44.000Z","msg":"你英文名多唔多人用？"